rules.natural: Provided that a Team observes a Cell, then the Project is successful.
A Team either observes a Cell or records a Video.
If a Team discovers a Protein, then the Team does not contaminate a Sample.
Under the condition that a Team isolates a Gene, the Team does not contaminate a Sample.
If a Team sequences DNA, then the Team discovers a Protein.
Under the condition that a Team maps a Genome, the Team isolates a Gene.
A Team either patents a Method or publishes Findings.
Whenever a Team publishes Findings, the Team maps a Genome.
Provided that a Reviewer validates an Experiment, then if a Team patents a Method, the Team sequences DNA.
A Reviewer either validates an Experiment or replicates Results.
Whenever a Reviewer replicates Results, then if a Team patents a Method, the Team sequences DNA.
Either a Device measures a Signal or detects an Anomaly.
Under the condition that a Device detects an Anomaly, the Project is successful.
If a Device malfunctions, then it is not the case that the Device is connected to a Network.
A Technician either repairs a Device or replaces a Device.
Whenever a Technician replaces a Device, the Device does not malfunction.
If an EthicsBoard approves a Protocol, then if a Technician repairs a Device, the Device does not malfunction.
Under the condition that a Journal accepts a Paper, the Journal prints an Issue.
Either a Journal accepts a Paper or, provided that the Project is not successful, an Author submits a Manuscript.
Whenever a Journal prints an Issue, the Journal distributes Copies.
If a Journal prints an Issue, then it is not the case that the Journal distributes Copies.
Provided that a Researcher presents at a Conference, then the Researcher operates a Microscope.
If a Researcher attends a Workshop, then either a Lab analyzes Data or, under the condition that the Lab does not use a Computer, the Lab calibrates a Sensor.
Provided that a Researcher trains a Student, then either a Lab analyzes Data or, if the Lab does not use a Computer, the Lab calibrates a Sensor.
Under the condition that a Researcher visits a Lab, the Researcher collaborates with an Institute.
A Researcher either visits a Lab or consults an Expert.
If a Researcher consults an Expert, then the Researcher either attends a Workshop or trains a Student.
Whenever a Lab acquires Equipment, then either the Lab analyzes Data or, provided that the Lab does not use a Computer, the Lab calibrates a Sensor.
Provided that a Lab upgrades Software, then the Lab maintains a Facility.
If a Researcher writes a Paper, then under the condition that the Project is not successful, the Researcher publishes in a Journal.
Either a Device is secure or, if a Device malfunctions, then the Device is connected to a Network.
If a Journal rejects a Paper, then it is not the case that the Journal accepts the Paper.
Either a Journal rejects a Paper or an Author revises a Paper.
Whenever an Author withdraws a Paper, then the Author does not resubmit the Paper.
If a Lab uses a Computer, then the Project is successful.
A Lab either models a Simulation or either analyzes Data or, if the Lab does not use a Computer, calibrates a Sensor.
If it is not the case that if a Team records a Video then the Project is successful, then the Team contaminates a Sample.
Provided that it is not the case that if a Device measures a Signal then the Project is successful, then the Device malfunctions.
Under the condition that it is not the case that either a Researcher presents at a Conference or writes a Paper, then the Researcher is funded by a Grant.
If it is not the case that either a Researcher presents at a Conference or writes a Paper, then it is not the case that the Researcher is funded by a Grant.
Provided that it is not the case that if a Device is tested then the Device is not secure, then the Device is reliable.
If it is not the case that if a Device is tested then the Device is not secure, then the Device is not reliable.
Under the condition that it is not the case that if an Author revises a Paper then the Journal does not accept the Paper, then the Author resubmits the Paper.
Provided that it is not the case that if an Author revises a Paper then the Journal does not accept the Paper, then the Author withdraws the Paper.
Whenever it is not the case that if it is not the case that either a Paper cites a Study or it is not the case that a Device malfunctions then the Paper is retracted, then the Paper is corrected.

Provided that it is not the case that if it is not the case that either a Paper cites a Study or it is not the case that a Device malfunctions then the Paper is retracted, then it is not the case that the Paper is corrected.
If it is not the case that a Lab acquires Equipment, then the Lab upgrades Software.
If the Project is not successful, then it is not the case that an Author submits a Manuscript.
